text: Luc Frieden (; born 16 September 1963) is a Luxembourgish politician and lawyer who is the 25th prime minister of Luxembourg since November 2023. He is a member of the Christian Social People's Party (CSV). In early 2023, he was elected to be the lead candidate of the CSV for the general elections in October. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Luxembourg Category:Current national leaders Category:Bankers Category:Lawyers
